Note: Top-level Let with non-constant initializer. __module_init runs the
Note: initializer before main's body. The global table must be a valid pointer.
Note: We write a value and read it back to confirm the allocation worked.
Note: Expected exit code: 42

Let MY_TABLE be allocate(64)

Process called "main" returns Integer:
    memory_set_integer(MY_TABLE, 0, 42)
    Let v be memory_get_integer(MY_TABLE, 0)
    Return v
End Process
